reviewText:
One of the classics of my childhood.

Ideal party game:
- local coop with one PC (best if you can play it on a big screen TV);
- fun, easy-to-pick-up gameplay;
- random and balanced enough in the end (especially with more than 2 players);
- ideal length (guaranteed to end soon after started with heated arguments).

I really liked the extent of customization available - just make sure not to waste too much time on creating teams or maps!
Recommend picking it up on a sale!
